===========================
Info
===========================
Map Name:fy_testbox_v1
Author:Masta
Added by:Masta
===========================
Installation
===========================
1.Extract all the files anywhere.(Recommended Desktop)
2.Copy the fy_testbox_v1.bsp and fy_testbox_v1.nav and paste it in your maps folder
Example:
C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\YOURUSERNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

And you are done,you just have to create your own server and find the map in the map list.
===========================
Notes
===========================
When you spawn you need to shoot that wood until it breaks or you can just press the red button.

This map included waypoints for bots so now you can play this map with bots :D!


Thanks to:
aleksandr for waypointing for cs:s bots tutorial.
